Comment: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:10.73,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Toda hora é uma missão
Comment: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:13.27,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Sorte ou azar? O destino dirá
Comment: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:15.71,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Ambições a mil
Comment: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.09,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Seja o que for, eu tiro de letra
Comment: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.35,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Só queria uma chance de mostrar quem eu sou
Comment: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:22.13,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Esse papo de "magia" não resolve nada
Comment: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:22.98,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Fico na minha e deixo isso pra lá
Comment: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:24.35,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Destino bate à porta, um capítulo ideal
Comment: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:25.33,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Ideias brotam sem parar
Comment: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:27.71,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Tirei a sorte grande, vou mandar bem, então bora lá!
Comment: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.10,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,O futuro está se transformando
Comment: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:35.12,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Quando eu despertar, nada poderá me parar
Comment: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:38.78,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Me dê um choque no coração!
Comment: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:41.25,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Até o sonho mais puro renasce agora
Comment: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.89,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Por tudo que é precioso, enfrente o passado
Comment: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.35,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Dia e noite, sigo a toda velocidade
Comment: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:47.28,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Ruja agora!
Comment: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.79,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Choque no coração!
Comment: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:51.10,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Mesmo quase desistindo, levanto de novo
Comment: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:53.72,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Nessa estrada sem fim, deixo o passado pra trás
Comment: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:56.16,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Mesmo contra o vento, sigo a toda velocidade
Comment: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:57.25,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Jamais recuarei!
Comment: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:59.69,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Um coração perdido na escuridão
Comment: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:02.35,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Esse grande mistério é subliminar
Comment: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.80,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Ninguém te conhece, mas lerei teu coração
Comment: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:07.19,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,O que vem pela frente vai ser daora?
Comment: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:09.70,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Luz e sombra, um pesadelo sem trégua
Comment: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:12.16,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,Sonhar em ser quem sou, nisso estou focado
Comment: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.60,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,No mundo que eu sempre quis, ouso e entro em sintonia
Comment: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:17.86,Translation,,0,0,0,kara,A história continua, realize seu sonho e seja o melhor!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Romaji,,0,0,0,,
